ARTIST GIFT: Our @UnitedCenter x @JeffHamilton designs for @champagnepapi & @21Savage celebrate the opening of their #ItsAllABlur tour in Chicago!

Each custom lambskin jacket is 1 of 1 for each artist and was left backstage at the shows. Swipe to see the features!

DRAKE:

🔵 The OVO owl is perched on the UC.

🔵 Chicago stars representing the location of the sold out shows at the United Center.

 🔵 Custom, autographed plaque inside the jacket celebrating Drake having the most concerts and tickets sold of any rapper in United Center history.

🔵 All 9 United Center shows Drake has played since 2013 with the tour art on the back.

21 SAVAGE:

🔵 21 Savage icons, including his name logo and dagger.

🔵 All 21 Savage albums listed on the left sleeve.
 
🔵 All Drake & 21 Savage collaborations listed on the right sleeve.

🔵 Custom, autographed plaque inside the jacket celebrating his 2023 debut shows at the United Center with the tour art on the back.

What do you think?

For this season’s Knicks collection, we worked with iconic leather jacket creator, Jeff Hamilton, to create a special piece limited to 100 units. 

This jacket is crafted from sheep leather and features various custom patches executed in multiple applications, including leather appliqué and direct satin stitch. The jacket also includes a fully stretched satin lining and comes in a custom garment bag with a certification of authenticity signed by Ronnie Fieg and Jeff Hamilton. 

The Kith & Jeff Hamilton for the New York Knicks Leather Varsity Jacket releases with the full collection tomorrow at Kith shops, 11AM EST on Kith.com, 11AM CET on EU.Kith.com & the Kith App.

Explore the full collection now via link in bio.
